msgid "home_hero_desc"
msgstr "Church community management system. From membership lists to all activities."

msgid "home_cta_desc"
msgstr "To access the churches interface and other sections, click on \"COMMUNAUTÉ\" (the icon or this button)"

msgid "about_intro"
msgstr "Communauté is an application or management system for churches and religious assemblies. It covers the following areas:"

msgid "about_item1"
msgstr "List of Churches, Groups, Regions"

msgid "about_item2"
msgstr "List of People: Adults, Youth and Children"

msgid "about_item3"
msgstr "Activity and worship session reports."

msgid "about_item4"
msgstr "Particularities: difficulties and projects."

msgid "about_item5"
msgstr "Light to the City: List of establishments, participants and studies."

msgid "about_item6"
msgstr "Sunday Messages, hymns and announcements."

msgid "about_desc"
msgstr "Communauté is designed to make the task easier for church leaders by giving them real-time and long-term information they need. It has a solid database, search bars, and a data filtering system by regions, groups, churches, sessions and dates. Certain information (the most important) is only accessible to leaders. Even churches cannot access each other's private data."

msgid "Les informations sur l'église."
msgstr "Church information."

msgid "svc_eglises_title"
msgstr "Churches"

msgid "svc_eglises_desc"
msgstr "The list and information (details) on churches along with filtering options (number of churches by group, region and national) and the ability to search a church by name."

msgid "svc_groupes_title"
msgstr "Groups"

msgid "svc_groupes_desc"
msgstr "The list of groups with additional information and, like the church, the ability to filter by region and national level with their count."

msgid "svc_bilans_title"
msgstr "Session Reports & More"

msgid "svc_bilans_desc"
msgstr "The list, filtering by session (Monday, Thursday and Sunday) to view sessions by group, region and total. Cell reports and special events."

msgid "svc_personnes_title"
msgstr "Members"

msgid "svc_personnes_desc"
msgstr "The list of Youth, Children and Adults with details and filters by district, group, region and national, with the ability to search a person by name."

msgid "svc_lumiere_title"
msgstr "Light to the City & Particularities"

msgid "svc_lumiere_desc"
msgstr "We have the list of establishments, participants and study reports. For particularities, church members can post their projects and difficulties."

msgid "svc_annonces_title"
msgstr "Announcements, Messages"

msgid "svc_annonces_desc"
msgstr "We have the list of announcements and messages with hymns for worship. This page displays the most recent announcements and messages."
